    "Lenoir petitioned the <em>Comit\u00e9 d'Instruction Publique</em> asking that the tomb of Francis I and all medieval statues be installed in his new museum to assist in French history.": [],
    "He amassed objects from all 83 <em>d\u00e9partements</em> of France.": [],
