    "After the fall of Napoleon and the restoration of the monarchy in 1815, <a href=\"/quatremeredequincya\">Antoine Quatrem\u00e8re de Quincy</a>, now the <em>Intendant G\u00e9n\u00e9ral des Arts et Monuments Publics</em>, attacked Lenoir and his activities in Quatrem\u00e8re's <em>Consid\u00e9rations morales</em>.": [],
