    "His art histories written to accompany his exhibitions (<em>Histoire des arts en France</em>) are among the first histories of costume and stained glass (Bazin).": [],
    "He is the key figure for the notion that objects are best contemplated in a museum atmosphere separate from their context.": [],
    "Then as now, the idea had its detractors.": [],
