    "However, the young Jules Michelet, later France's great romantic historian, found Lenoir's museum \"the eternal continuity of the nation,\" a walking experience of French history, Merovingians through to the Enlightenment and his present day, via sculpture, furniture, and tapestries (Schama).": [
